{ 16...Bxf5  17.Ng5!  Nf6  18.Bg2  Kh8  19.Ne6!  Bxe6  20.dxe6  Black is lost, as he is already defeated on the light squares. White's e-pawn is very annoying and Black's queen's rook is short of squares. }
