13. Nxe4 fxe4 14. Ng5 Nf5 15. Nxe4 Bh6 { 15...Nd4  16.Bd3  Bf5  17.Be3± } 16.
Bb2
{ White doesn't allow Black to exchange his problem-piece, which is cutting a lot of thin air from its current position. }
16... Nd4 { There is no alternative way to activate the pieces. } 17. Bxd4 exd4
18. Bg4 Bg7 19. h3
{ Black managed to upgrade his dark-squared bishop, but he has to worry about the d-pawn and the square e6. }
