24. Rd1 Ng8 25. Nh5 Nf5 26. Nb5 Ra8 27. Qe6 Qxe6
{ 27...Rfd8  28.Qxd7  Rxd7  29.g4  Nh4  30.c5+-  White will penetrate Black's queenside. }
