Ra3 Kh8 { Now, White is especially motivated to lift the rook to the h-file. }
17. Rh3 f4 18. Ne6 Bxe6 19. dxe6 Qe7 20. Bf3 Rb8 21. Ba3
{ Freezing the c-pawn is a very important strategic element. } 21... Kg8 22.
Bd5
{ Obviously, White is in full control and might progress with Kh1, Rg1 and g4-g5. }
