20... c6 21. Ne3 d5 { 21...Kh8  22.Rd3  d5  23.cxd5  cxd5  24.Ba3+- } 22. cxd5
cxd5 23. Rb3 { Activating two pieces at once. } 23... Rxa4
{ 23...Qc8  24.Ba3+-   23...d4  24.Ba3+- } 24. Rxb7 Ra8
{ 24...Ra1  25.Nc2  Ra2  26.Ba3+- } 25. Qc2
{ There is always a way to exploit this king on h7. } 25... Nfg8 26. g4 Rc8 27.
Qb1 Rb8 { 27...e4  28.Ba3+- } 28. Rxb8 Qxb8 29. Ba3
