{ 21...b5  22.Qe7+- } 22. Qf6 Ra6 { 22...Qd7  23.Bc4+- } 23. Bxa6 Qxa6 24. Qe7
Qc6 25. Qg5 Qe8 26. h4
{ Improving White's king safety and at the same time reducing Black's, as h5 will follow. }
