18. exf5 gxf5 19. Nh4
{ A very important motif. The knight is getting in touch with Black's weaknesses. The placement of Black's h-pawn makes this move particularly effective. }
19... Nc7 { 19...Nxd5?  20.Nxf5+- } 20. Qc1
