{ Global thinking is a trademark of the Bayonet. The missing g-pawn makes both, h4 and h5 formidable outposts for the knights. }
25... Ne8 26. Bc2 Qd7 27. Rg3 f4 { 27...Kh7  28.Nxg7  Nxg7  29.Bxh6+- } 28.
Bxf4 exf4 29. Nxf4
{ Black's cramped pieces cannot handle five fully mobile attackers. } 29...
Rxa4 30. Nh5 Ra2 31. Qxh6 Rxc2 32. Rxe8+ *

