{ 18.g3  , as in 1-0 @@StartBracket@@38@@EndBracket@@ Zentai, P @@StartBracket@@2311@@EndBracket@@-Pammer Zagroczky, G @@StartBracket@@1937@@EndBracket@@ Balatonalmadi 2011 was also clearly better for White, but not the maximum which can be achieved. White can do without this weakening pawn move, as the knight can be tolerated on the f4-square. }
