24. Kh1 Ra8 25. Bc1 { Mobilizing the knight, as Black threatened a perpetual. }
25... e4 { 25...Qh5+  26.Nh2+- } 26. Nh2 Qf5 27. Rg1
{ And White is just winning on the kingside. } *

