23. g4 { Winning the battle of the light squares, again. } 23... Bxe4 24. Bxe4
Qf6 25. c6
{ White is imposing a weakness on Black's position, exploiting the fact, that  25...b6  doesn't work due to the unprotected rook. }
25... Rb8 26. cxb7 Rxb7 27. a6 Rb8 { 27...Rb6  28.Bc2+- } 28. Rf3
{ Liquidating into a completely won ending. } 28... Qg5 29. Qxg5 hxg5 30. Rxf7
Kxf7 31. Rc1 { Finally harvesting the fruits from move 25. } 31... Rc8 32. Bd3
