{ Once more, this is the most active place for the queen's rook. In the game 1-0 @@StartBracket@@56@@EndBracket@@ Farago, I @@StartBracket@@2462@@EndBracket@@-Havasi, G @@StartBracket@@2274@@EndBracket@@ Budapest 2014, White choose  18.Rc1  instead. }
18... Nf5 19. h3
{ A multi-purpose move. White is creating air for his king, waits for information and prepares a potential g2-g4. }
19... Bd7 20. c5 Bb5
