{ This final chapter deals with all the rare lines, which are rare for a reason. }
9... Bg4
{ While it is true that this bishop is mostly short of squares, exchanging it for the knight without compensation is a mistake, as this surrenders the light squares. }
10. Be3
{ The bishop is hardly seen on this square, as it would normally provoke ...Ng4. After the premature advance  10.c5?  , Black can reach equality with  10...c6  , a rare bird in the Bayonet. }
